beer.beer_description:
ABV may vary for lisenced brews.
Faxe Premium is a classic international premium lager with a smooth, distinctive taste. The combination of the finest malt, hops and own water results in a all-malt premium beer, which is full-bodied, but at the same time pleasantly mild with a round taste and a smooth mouthfeel. A crisp and well-balanced lager beer.
